Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.41,0:00:04.65,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,700)}Murder File: The Long-Armed-Bat-White-Flying-Squirrel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:10.09,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,The victim, the long-armed-bat-white-flying-squirrel's time of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:11.42,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...was 10 o'clock last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.06,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,A knife in the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:15.13,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:18.20,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Everything was locked\Nfrom the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.20,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,There's no trace of\Nthe killer's getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.20,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,A locked room, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:23.34,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:24.37,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,What else do we know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:29.54,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,The knife was covered with the fingerprints of a ramen shop employee living next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:31.38,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,That's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:34.51,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Detective Hamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:35.65,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:38.15,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Around 7 o'clock last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:38.65,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:40.82,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...the person in apartment\N201 next door...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:46.32,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...asked me to ask you if Mr. Long-Armed-Bat-White-Flying-Squirrel and a child were kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:50.16,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,They really asked that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.16,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,They really asked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:52.90,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I made up an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:54.63,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.54,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I just got some new information!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:01.44,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:03.21,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,According to the\Napartment manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:05.18,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...the victim was never in\Nhis room at night time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:08.05,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.48,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...the victim was nocturnal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:10.32,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:12.15,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,The crime took place in daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:13.79,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:15.95,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...he was carried here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:17.76,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I was told to tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:21.06,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:22.53,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:24.53,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I like your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:29.67,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,- Detective Hamada!\N- What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:31.34,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I just learned something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:31.90,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:35.14,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I talked with the head girl at a\Nsnack bar the victim often visited...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:39.41,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...and she seemed disappointed that his arms weren't as long as everyone makes them out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:41.55,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:44.32,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,This is completely\Nfabricated information...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:49.19,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...apparently the victim said "As\Nlong as I have long arms, I won't\Nlet those bastards do as they like."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:51.06,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:51.42,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:52.96,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,According to what I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:55.33,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,..."It's good to let those\Nbastards do what they want"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:56.36,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Apparently the victim said this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:59.16,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Whichever one it is just\Nwho are "those bastards"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.40,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Who are "those bastards"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:01.57,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:03.47,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I want to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:06.74,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.54,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...this is from the\Ncouple living next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:09.21,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:12.71,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Apparently the victim sang\None of his hometown songs\Nin a loud vo ice last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:14.21,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,What hometown song?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.21,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I'm a little bit unsure on that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:18.48,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I'd have sex with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:21.55,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Can I mention one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:22.32,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.12,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,According to his coworker...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:28.13,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...the victim apparently said\N"If you kill me, lock everything\Nfrom the inside and kill me."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:29.56,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.06,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,According to what I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:34.90,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...he apparently always stressed that\Nhe never did anything like lock things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:39.34,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Hmm, well we can't know the\Nlayout of the room in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:43.28,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Well, the owner stated it's a 15-tatami mat size when he advertised the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.41,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Does the owner look suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:49.55,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,No, he moved to\NAustralia 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:50.95,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,He's the prime minister there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:54.49,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:55.85,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.72,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,There's a hidden door over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:58.39,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.49,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,There's a child inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.26,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.76,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I'm saying an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:04.73,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:05.93,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,- Let's take a look.\N- Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:07.60,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.67,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,That's my private thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.07,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,I like your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:14.97,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:15.94,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:17.21,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...let's start again at step one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.55,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.12,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,...just what happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.05,GOTTSU,,0,0,0,,Hey, me... I'm... I have no clue.
